# Normalize every text file to LF in the repo and on checkout on all platforms.
# chezmoi applies source bytes verbatim, so LF keeps the shell scripts and templates
# it deploys to Linux working; PowerShell, AutoHotkey, oh-my-posh, and JSON all tolerate
# LF on Windows. This prevents CRLF-in-.sh breakage for anyone who forks the repo.
* text=auto eol=lf
